TEXT_ORIGINAL: ［エルフ特製すぺしゃるでぃすく］
●ゲームの中のイベントをクリアー　　　　●　ゲーム中の曲をもう一度聞きたい
TEXT_LITERAL_ENGLISH: ●Clear the event in the game　　　　●I want to hear the song in the game

TEXT_ORIGINAL: した女の子にもう一度あいたい
TEXT_LITERAL_ENGLISH: Want to meet the girl who did again
column9: Note that this is a run-on sentence from the first option, above. Basically, it lets you select the not-safe-for-work slideshow of girls from the game.

TEXT_LITERAL_ENGLISH: A long section with embedded strings with all of the names of the .MES files in the disk 1 directory.
